<p>He graduated from İstanbul University Faculty of Communications in 1992. He worked as an assistant in İstanbul University Management Faculty between 1994-1996. Between 1996-2000 he worked at a private educational consulting firm. Between 2000-2003 he worked as an assistant in Bilgi University Management Faculty. Between 1995-2010 he became one of the founders and members of board of Community Volunteers Foundation and ÇEKÜL Foundation. He has been working as a partner of Webdenal.com since 2005.</p>